---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hooking Point">
	<div class="hero-bg">
		<div class="page hero">
			<p class="tagline">(회사 소개 한 줄 작성 예정 — 알려주시면 반영할게요)</p>

			<div class="axes">
				<a class="axis" href="/filmography">
					<span class="axis-label">01 · EDITING</span>
					<h2>편집</h2>
					<p>드라마·영화·광고·다큐를 넘나들며 이야기의 리듬을 설계합니다.</p>
					<span class="axis-link">EDITING / WORKS 보기 →</span>
				</a>
				<a class="axis" href="/ip-development">
					<span class="axis-label">02 · IP DEVELOPMENT</span>
					<h2>IP기획</h2>
					<p>편집실에서 쌓은 이야기 감각으로 새로운 오리지널 IP를 기획합니다.</p>
					<span class="axis-link">IP DEVELOPMENT 보기 →</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.hero-bg {
		background:
			radial-gradient(640px circle at 12% 15%, rgba(42, 59, 143, 0.1), transparent 60%),
			radial-gradient(560px circle at 88% 55%, rgba(255, 107, 74, 0.09), transparent 60%);
	}
	.hero {
		padding-top: 4rem;
		padding-bottom: 6rem;
	}
	.tagline {
		max-width: 34rem;
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: var(--heading);
		margin: 0 0 4rem;
	}
	.axes {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}
	@media (max-width: 700px) {
		.axes {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
	.axis {
		background: var(--surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow);
		transition: border-color 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
	}
	.axis:hover {
		border-color: var(--accent);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	.axis-label {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--heading);
	}
	.axis h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}
	.axis p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--muted);
	}
	.axis-link {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--heading);
	}
</style>
